---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
    title="Intermediate Tutorial: Flight Engineer - ESP32 Drone"
    description="ESP32 Drone intermediate tutorial. Learn code modification, PID tuning, and sensor integration."
    lang="en"
>
    <header style="background: white; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 1rem 2rem;">
        <nav style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: center;">
            <a href="/" style="font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.25rem; color: var(--text-dark);">ESP32 Drone</a>
            <div style="display: flex; gap: 2rem;">
                <a href="/">Home</a>
                <a href="/tutorials" style="font-weight: 600;">Tutorials</a>
                <a href="/hardware">Hardware</a>
                <a href="/downloads">Downloads</a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="/zh/tutorials/intermediate">中文</a>
            </div>
        </nav>
    </header>
    
    <main style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 2rem; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 250px 1fr; gap: 2rem;">
        <!-- Sidebar -->
        <aside style="border-right: 1px solid var(--border); padding-right: 1rem;">
            <h3 style="margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-light);">Course Levels</h3>
            <nav style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
                <a href="/tutorials" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Beginner: Flight Explorer</a>
                <a href="/tutorials/intermediate" style="font-size: 0.9rem; font-weight: 600;">Intermediate: Flight Engineer</a>
                <a href="/tutorials/advanced" style="font-size: 0.9rem;">Advanced: Flight Scientist</a>
            </nav>
        </aside>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div>
            <div style="margin-bottom: 2rem; padding-bottom: 1rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);">
                <span style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #D97706; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600;">Intermediate Level</span>
                <h1 style="margin: 0.5rem 0;">Flight Engineer</h1>
                <p style="color: var(--text-medium);">Modify code, understand flight control algorithms</p>
                <p style="margin-top: 0.5rem; color: var(--text-light); font-size: 0.9rem;">
                    Requires basic C programming knowledge.<br>
                    Duration: 1-2 months.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div style="background: #DBEAFE; border: 1px solid #93C5FD; border-radius: var(--radius); padding: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                <strong>Note:</strong> The complete English tutorial is being translated. For full content, please check the <a href="/zh/tutorials/intermediate">Chinese version</a>.
            </div>

            <section style="margin-bottom: 2rem;">
                <h2 style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">What You'll Learn</h2>
                <ul style="padding-left: 1.5rem;">
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Code modification and compilation with ESP-IDF</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">PID controller tuning</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Sensor data processing (MPU6050, BMP280)</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Wi-Fi telemetry and real-time plotting</li>
                    <li style="margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Ultrasonic obstacle avoidance</li>
                </ul>
            </section>

            <section style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem;">
                <a href="/zh/tutorials/intermediate" style="background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: var(--radius); font-weight: 600;">View Chinese Version</a>
            </section>
        </div>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer style="background: var(--primary); color: white; padding: 2rem; margin-top: 4rem;">
        <div style="max-width: 1200px; margin: 0 auto; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem;">
            <!-- Contact -->
            <div>
                <h4 style="margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">Contact Us</h4>
                <div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.5rem;">
                    <a href="https://wa.me/8618601106543" target="_blank" style="color: white; text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
                        <span>📱</span> WhatsApp: +86 18601106543
                    </a>
                    <div style="display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
                        <span>💬</span> WeChat: +86 18601106543
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Social -->
            <div>
                <h4 style="margin-bottom: 1rem; font-size: 1.1rem;">YouTube</h4>
                <a href="https://www.youtube.com/@imagrove" target="_blank" style="color: white; text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.5rem;">
                    <span>▶️</span> @imagrove
                </a>
            </div>

            <!-- Copyright -->
            <div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-end;">
                <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; opacity: 0.8;">© 2026 ESP32 Drone. All rights reserved.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </footer>
</Layout>
